IOStream by example

* Introduction 
 
 Streams are potentially infinite iterable objects that have a very rich interface and
  perform most operations in a lazy manner and functional style. Staccatissimo-IO exploits their power to 
  easily perform complex transformations on directories, files and streams.   
  
