** Filtering and Counting 
   
+---
  Reader in = ...
  
  // How many words start with "A"? 
  IOStreams
    .fromWords(in)
    .filter(Strings.startsWith("A"))
    .size();  
+---

** Mapping and Testing all

+---
 InpuStream in = ...   
  
 //Do all lines have less than 100 characters? 
 IOStreams
    .fromLines(in)
    .map(Strings.length())
    .all(lessThan(100); 

+---  

** Skipping and printing

+-- 
  Redable in = ...;
  
  //Print each token delimited by "|", except of spaces " "  
  IOStreams
    .fromTokens(in, "|")
    .skip(" ")
    .each(IO.println());
+-- 